                    <span>I found "Embracing the Fear" by Judith Bemis and Amr Barrada to be much more helpful.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not bad...but nothing to set it above the pack...</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>6</span>
